OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,FITV News Reporter David Chisnall was
OL,7,Fat the route reveal announcement along
OL,8,Fwith local politicians and cyclists.
OL,10,FThe route has been revealed for the
OL,11,FTour de France Femmes 2027, which will
OL,12,Fsee some of the world's best cyclists
OL,13,Fpass through Greater Manchester.
OL,15,FIt is the first-ever team time trial
OL,16,Fin the history of the Tour de France
OL,17,FFemmes and the first time both the
OL,18,Fmen's and women's Grand Departs have
OL,19,Ftaken place in the same country
OL,20,Foutside France.
OL,26,@zD@Zrr
