OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776773466
OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,FManchester was announced as the Stage
OL,7,FOne finish and Stage Two start of the
OL,8,Fwomen's competition in January 2026.
OL,10,FStage One will be from Leeds to
OL,11,FManchester
OL,13,FStage 2 will be from Manchester to
OL,14,FSheffield
OL,16,FAfter travelling through Meltham in
OL,17,FWest Yorkshire, cyclists will arrive
OL,18,Fin Oldham as they ride along Dove
OL,19,FStone Reservoir.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
