OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,FThe men's race will also pass through
OL,7,Fthe region in 2027, through
OL,8,FLancashire, Greater Manchester and
OL,9,FLiverpool.
OL,11,FCouncillor Bev Craig, Leader of
OL,12,FManchester City Council, said: "Being
OL,13,Fable to watch the world's best
OL,14,Fcyclists in action and in such an
OL,15,Ficonic event, taking place right here
OL,16,Fon our doorstep in the heart of
OL,17,FManchester next summer, is going to be
OL,18,Fepic on so many levels.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
