PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776773466
OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,F"Championing women and girls to
OL,7,Fparticipate in and enjoy sports -
OL,8,Fincluding cycling - at all levels from
OL,9,Fentry through to elite, is really
OL,10,Fimportant to us and next year's Tour
OL,11,Fde France Femmes is set to play a huge
OL,12,Fpart in helping inspire the next
OL,13,Fgeneration of sporting talent from our
OL,14,Fcity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
