PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776773466
OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,F"With millions of spectators expected
OL,7,Fto line the routes, including here in
OL,8,Fthe city centre, we'll be going all
OL,9,Fout to help ensure the event's success
OL,10,Fwith what is set to be a 'Tour
OL,11,Ftakeover' of the city to maximise
OL,12,Fopportunities for local people and
OL,13,Fbusinesses to get involved, to grow
OL,14,Ftheir own sporting skills, and to take
OL,15,Fpart in the many community activities
OL,16,Fbeing planned."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
