PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776773466
OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,FDame Sarah Storey, Active Travel
OL,7,FCommissioner for Greater Manchester,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Greater Manchester hosting the
OL,9,Fopening stages of the Tour de France
OL,10,FFemmes is a huge opportunity for
OL,11,Feveryone who lives, works and will
OL,12,Fvisit here during that time, and we
OL,13,Fare expecting excitement to grow even
OL,14,Ffurther, especially now we know the
OL,15,Froute the Grand Depart will take
OL,16,Fthrough our city-region.
OL,26,@wD@Rrr
