PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776773466
OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,F"Seeing the competitors of the world's
OL,7,Fbiggest women's cycling race right up
OL,8,Fclose, as they weave their way through
OL,9,FManchester, Stockport, Rochdale and
OL,10,FOldham, will be incredibly inspiring
OL,11,Ffor people of all ages and the
OL,12,Fbenefits to local communities and
OL,13,Ffuture generations of riders will be
OL,14,Ffar reaching.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
