FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776773466
OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,F"Hosting both a finish and a start
OL,7,Fmeans that everyone visiting the city
OL,8,Fcentre will have an incredible
OL,9,Fopportunity to be close at hand to the
OL,10,Fpre and post-race action too,
OL,11,Fsomething that is truly unique in the
OL,12,Fsport of cycling.
OL,14,F"Hosting the first two days of the
OL,15,FGrand Depart not only shines a global
OL,16,Fspotlight on women's cycling, it
OL,17,Fboosts visibility for elite sport and
OL,18,Fthe opportunities available that
OL,19,Fencourage more women and girls to see
OL,20,Fcycling as something for them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
