PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776773466
OL,3,CManchester leg of Tour de France
OL,4,CFemmes 2027 revealed
OL,6,F"I'm excited to see the legacy of this
OL,7,Fhistoric event and with all the work
OL,8,Fbeing done in preparation for the
OL,9,Farrival of "Le Tour", know it will be
OL,10,Ffelt in Greater Manchester for years
OL,11,Fto come."
OL,13,FThe race will start in Leeds on 30
OL,14,FJuly, going to Manchester and
OL,15,FSheffield before ending on the Mall in
OL,16,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
